               <p>THOMAS BURCHFIELD. I am a <rs id="t18290611-54-viclabel280" type="occupation">scale-beam maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-54-victim473 t18290611-54-viclabel280"></join>. On the 28th of May, about two o'clock in the afternoon, I saw this scale safe in my shop, and a little after eight I was told it was gone - I ran out, saw the prisoner running, and one of my young men stopped him; I saw the scale taken from under his coat - he could reach it from the door; he appeared to be drunk or stupid.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290611-54-person474">
